      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/us-producer-prices-rose-slightly-more-than-forecast-in-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国生产者价格指数 8 月份较上月数据下调后略有回升，进一步表明通胀压力正在缓和。]]></description>
